Dataset Structure

The dataset is organized into modality-wise and center-wise folders, each containing images and their corresponding ground truth annotations:

PolypDB Modality Based Structure

├── BLI/
│ ├── images/
│ └── annotations/
├── FICE/
│ ├── images/
│ └── annotations/
├── LCI/
│ ├── images/
│ └── annotations/
├── NBI/
│ ├── images/
│ └── annotations/
└── WLI/
├── images/
└── annotations/

PolypDB Center-wise Structure

├── Simula/
│ ├── images/
│ ├── annotations/
│ └── bounding_boxes/
├── Karolinska/
│ ├── images/
│ ├── annotations/
│ └── bounding_boxes/
└── Vietnam/
├── images/
├── annotations/
└── bounding_boxes/
